data.description:
Home away from home!! This beautiful cabin-style property is just minutes away from Beaver Lake and a
small pond on the property. With lovely wildlife all around you, this dream home has large oversized
windows. The open living area features 2 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and 1 half bath. Extra storage on
the property. This property offers so much potential! Boat ramp is just minutes away on the same street!
